1. Don't listen on import (#10) — blocks testing.
2. Global error + 404 handlers (#1, #2) — prevents info leaks.
3. `helmet` + disable `x-powered-by` (#3) — one-line wins.
4. Rate limiting (#4) and body size limit (#5).
5. Validation scaffolding (#6) before adding any input-taking routes.
6. Auth on `/users` (#7) before deploying.

