  const parsed = UserQuerySchema.safeParse(req.query);
  if (!parsed.success) {
    return res.status(400).json({ error: 'Invalid query', details: parsed.error.flatten() });
  }
  // ...
});
```

## 3. Security Hardening

| Concern | Recommendation |
|---|---|
| Common HTTP headers (XSS, clickjacking, MIME sniffing) | `app.use(require('helmet')())` |
| CORS | Explicitly configure `cors()` with an allowlist rather than defaulting open |
